{"tid":1816421,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"聽返一首歌覺得好夾而家嘅香港，所以整咗條MV","createTime":"2020-01-08T08:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T16:27:35.000Z","uid":75671,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"db4f28110af8437745fd325cb97a01478b73baf0","tid":1816421,"uid":75671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T08:32:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zL408Cw0HUM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzL408Cw0HUM&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IsjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=5ea72db3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zL408Cw0HUM</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然係連詩雅<br />\n但唔知點解一聽就會諗起而家嘅香港<br />\n所以就心血來潮整咗條MV<br />\n希望可以鼓勵吓香港人<br />\n希望大家會鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實小弟都幾鍾意整MV<br />\n如果各位手足有啲咩歌都覺得同而家好夾<br />\n都可以同我講！<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！"},{"pid":"2e3d61a798bfc62a464e30225760829873c334ba","tid":1816421,"uid":75671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T08:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61908745fa8e809caa021f8b1948e064c20a40b1","tid":1816421,"uid":75671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T08:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0126f752e1ad8ec4b885b949a1c73ed1368f32","tid":1816421,"uid":75671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc07bb76585b84b7a3a8bd00923fbb14c870427","tid":1816421,"uid":268820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌推唔郁，留名鼓勵。加油﹗"},{"pid":"4c899f9150a601d4ffdc78273c6a1d0eabb99a37","tid":1816421,"uid":2